name: TD Global Technology Innovators Index ETF
longDescription: TD Global Technology Innovators Index ETF seeks to track, to the extent reasonably possible and before the deduction of fees and expenses, the performance of a technology innovators index. TD Global Technology Innovators Index ETF seeks to track, to the extent reasonably possible and before the deduction of fees and expenses, the performance of a technology innovators index which measures the investment return of technology companies that are deemed to be innovators based on higher annual growth rates in revenue, return on invested capital and operating margin expansion relative to their peers, while eliminating mega-cap technology stocks that typically dominate an index.
